"system:"
msgstr "vllm-ascend 使用以下环境变量来配置系统："

#: ../../source/user_guide/configuration/env_vars.md:5
msgid ""
"**Note:** Some environment variables are being migrated to `--additional-"
"config` options. These environment variables are still supported during "
"the migration period, and it is recommended to use `--additional-config` "
"for new deployments. See [Additional Configuration](additional_config.md)"
" for details."
msgstr ""
"**注意：** 部分环境变量正在迁移至 `--additional-config` "
"选项。迁移期间这些环境变量仍受支持，建议新部署使用 `--additional-config`。"
"详情请参阅[附加配置](additional_config.md)。"